# Alerting MVP Rule

This service uses lightweight in-memory alert aggregation.

Do not add Kafka, RabbitMQ, Redis, Elasticsearch, or persistent log storage for MVP.

Alert flow:

1. Log event ingested

2. Token validates app

3. ERROR logs are added to AlertAggregationService

4. Scheduler drains buckets on configured interval

5. Sends one summarized alert to enabled Slack/Discord destinations

INFO/WARN logs should not alert unless explicitly requested.

Alert failures should not fail log ingestion.